{"tid":2116194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵九龍灣車廠承辦商員工確診","createTime":"2020-07-20T04:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T05:29:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c422844aae72aa48483bdcb615ef715dda0854","tid":2116194,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"港鐵昨日接獲承辦商通知，一名九龍灣車廠工場工作的承辦商員工確診，該名承辦商員工的家人早前亦證實確診，其在本月14日出現病徵後，15日已沒有上班。<br />\n港鐵指已即時安排為工場範圍、員工餐廳等進行徹底清潔和消毒，亦已要求與該承辦商員工有密切接觸的職員，接受深喉唾液測試，以及留在家中直至測試結果證明健康。港鐵總部大樓全體員工今日在家工作。據悉該名確診承辦商員工居住於慈雲山慈愛苑，屬於家庭感染群組。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e4%b9%9d%e9%be%8d%e7%81%a3%e8%bb%8a%e5%bb%a0%e6%89%bf%e8%be%a6%e5%95%86%e5%93%a1%e5%b7%a5%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba-227221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e4%25b9%259d%25e9%25be%258d%25e7%2581%25a3%25e8%25bb%258a%25e5%25bb%25a0%25e6%2589%25bf%25e8%25be%25a6%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba-227221&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=2ef02c19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e4%b9%9d%e9%be%8d%e7%81%a3%e8%bb%8a%e5%bb%a0%e6%89%bf%e8%be%a6%e5%95%86%e5%93%a1%e5%b7%a5%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba-227221</a>"},{"pid":"0caec13a353273dcb4790fdd0669c9da36e16e5b","tid":2116194,"uid":273991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"黨鐵感染群組go go go <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d94ab2acaecbd93ba610564895d7219b3367